Description_lang: Join the Forsaken war machine as it marches on Hillsbrad Foothills for the Horde!
Drive the night elves from Ashenvale and claim its resources for the Horde!
Adventure inside the Wailing Caverns and fight the wicked Druids of the Fang.
Explore the abandoned mines beneath Westfall where the Defias Brotherhood musters its outlaw army.
A ruined keep overlooking Silverpine Forest, this dark fortress serves as home to a cabal of fallen Gilnean nobility.
Claim Warsong Gulch for the Horde in this capture-the-flag battleground.
Fight Alliance players for control of Arathi Basin in this resource-race battleground.
Battle the dark cult known as the Searing Blade inside the volcanic caverns beneath Orgrimmar!
Run a random Warlords of Draenor dungeon to upgrade your character's gear!
Battle other players inside a Random Battleground!
Aid the Forsaken High Command in conquering the port of Gilneas for the Horde!
Join the invasion fleet to secure a new island off the coast of the Alliance capital of Stormwind!
Deathwing's minions have begun an assault on the World Tree. Our allies, the Cenarion Circle, need your help!
Thrall and the Earthen Ring need your aid in assaulting the elemental plane of Deepholm!
Join the Forsaken war machine as it marches on Hillsbrad Foothills for the Horde!
Your help is needed to secure the Northern Barrens against the encroaching quilboars and centaurs!
Aid in driving back the encroaching Alliance forces and assist in securing Azshara for the glory of the Horde!
Join the Horde forces fighting against the renegade Grimtotems who dominate Thousand Needles.
Help the Horde and the Bilgewater Cartel establish a presence in Tanaris before the Alliance does!
Help the Horde secure the great forest of Feralas against the Alliance and the Grimtotems.
Provide aid to the Marshal Expeditions' personnel as they uncover the secrets of Un'Goro Crater.
Our Cenarion allies need your aid in their battle to turn back Twilight's Hammer in Silithus.
The Horde forces in Stonetalon Mountains need your help to drive back the Alliance invaders and protect our people.
The Cenarion Circle requires your help to wrest Felwood from the control of demons and other corrupt creatures!
Donova Snowden may have discovered the key to dealing with the Winterfall furbolg threat in Winterspring once and for all
The brave Horde warriors of Desolace need your help to beat back the armies of the Alliance and ancient demons.
With the recent Alliance victories in the Barrens, our enemies are threatening to cut our supply lines.  They must be stopped!
Dustwallow Marsh is overrun with enemies of many kinds and the Alliance forces there are dangerously strong.
Ancient texts tell us that Uldum is home to untold riches and treasures beyond compare. Claim these in the name of the Horde!
Your help is needed to turn back the numberless Scourge invaders and secure the help of the Forsaken in fighting the Scourge.
The Dark Lady's forces need your help to expand the dominions of the Horde and drive back the Alliance.
The Wildhammer dwarves of the Hinterlands have officially thrown in their lot with the Alliance and must be defeated!
The Alliance forces are advancing into the ruined city of Andorhal. Stop them before they can gain a foothold there!
The Argent Crusade has reinforced its presence in the Eastern Plaguelands and it needs your help to consolidate its victories.
The Alliance is desperate to gain a foothold in the Badlands. Keep them at bay at all costs!
The Shattered Hand reports that the Dark Iron dwarves of the Searing Gorge seem to be preparing for war.
Eitrigg's son, Ariok, needs your assistance to halt the blind aggression of the Blackrock orcs.
Okrilla, commander of the Horde forces at Dreadmaul Hold, requires your help to secure the outpost against rebellious ogres.
Persuade Trade Baron Silversnap to continue supplying the Horde with weapons and munitions!
The commander in Northern Stranglethorn Vale requires your aid to keep the supply routes open.
Our forces in the Cape of Stranglethorn require your help to deal with the pirates and naga who have overrun the jungle.
Your skills are needed to fight the Burning Legion's presence on the shattered remnants of Outland.
The Warsong Offensive in Northrend needs your help to overcome the continued threat from the undead Scourge.
The Warchief requires your help to prepare for an assault on the Twilight Highlands!
Alliance forces in the Redridge Mountains are spread too thin and need your help.
Our new brothers in the Alliance need your help to fend off the aggressive Horde offensive in their beloved homeland.
The crime rate of Westfall has skyrocketed as people fight for shelter and food. If you want to help the Alliance, this would be a good place to start.
The citizens of Duskwood are in dire need of your assistance!
Recent attacks by the Horde on our trade ships off the coast of Stormwind Harbor must be met with swift and just force!
Your help is needed at Mount Hyjal. The Cenarion Circle reports that Deathwing's minions have launched a destructive offensive against the world tree!
The Earthen Ring requires our aid! They report that the elemental plane of Deepholm threatens to overtake our world and destroy all life on Azeroth!
The people of Lor'danel need your aid in securing their town against the Twilight's Hammer.
The Horde's aggression in Ashenvale cannot be allowed to stand! Repel the invaders and restore the sacred forest.
The sentinels of Thousand Needles need your help to turn back the marauding Grimtotem raiders who dominate the area.
The Alliance needs your help to win concessions from the local baron of Tanaris and access to the desert's priceless resources.
The Alliance forces of Feralas need your help to overcome our enemies, the Horde and the Grimtotems.
The Alliance needs you to provide support to the Marshal Expeditions as they uncover the secrets of Un'Goro Crater.
Our Cenarion Circle allies in Silithus require your assistance to fight back against the Twilight's Hammer onslaught.
The brave soldiers of the Desolace are beset by demons and the armies of the Horde, and they need your help.
The Horde's forces are poised to push into Stonetalon and they must be opposed!
The Emerald Sanctuary requires your help to redeem Felwood from the demonic influences that rule the forest.
Donova Snowden in Winterspring requires your help to overcome the threat of the Winterfall furbolg.
Alliance soldiers have made tremendous gains in the Southern Barrens. Your efforts are needed to consolidate their victory!
You must aid SI:7's Calia Hastings in uncovering the threats to Theramore, both within the city and beyond its walls.
Be one of the first to enter glorious Uldum and claim its treasures in honor of the Alliance!
The people of Bloodmyst need your help to deal with treacherous blood elves and dangerous creatures loose on the island.
In the wake of the cataclysm's destruction, Wetlands has become overrun with wild beasts, orcish raiders, and savage gnolls!
The destruction of the Stonewrought Dam has the dwarven mountaineers stretched thin. Reinforcements are desperately needed!
Your aid is needed in Arathi Highlands. Ancient Stromgarde's honor must be redeemed!

On the heels of our early victories in Andorhal, the Forsaken have decided to launch a counterattack. Your help is needed to beat back the Scourge and Horde and reclaim lost Andorhal in the Western Plaguelands.
The Argent Crusade needs your help to win back the Eastern Plaguelands from the grasp of the Scourge.
Your help is needed to survey the damage done by Deathwing, and the disposition of Horde forces in the Badlands.
SI:7 reports that the Dark Iron dwarves of the Searing Gorge are preparing to attack. Stop them before it's too late!
Your aid is urgently needed to put an end to the Blackrock orc menace in the Burning Steppes!
Nethergarde's garrison urgently needs your help to stem the Horde advance into the Blasted Lands!
The Alliance needs you to secure a steady supply of munitions from the Trade Baron Silversnap in the Swamp of Sorrows!
Years after Colonel Kurzen's treachery against Stormwind, his fate remains a mystery. Aid the survivors in learning what became of the colonel.
The Explorers' League expedition in the Cape of Stranglethorn needs your help to safeguard its site and findings from marauding ogres.
The expeditionary forces require your help to overcome the demonic armies of the Burning Legion that are invading from Outland!
The Valiance Expedition needs your help in Northrend to keep the forces of the Scourge under control and safeguard civilized lands!
King Wrynn requires a trustworthy and proven hero for a mission of the utmost importance.
Present yourself at Grommash Hold to swear an oath of allegiance to the new Warchief!
The locals have spoken of a powerful pandaren monk travelling into the Valley of the Four Winds. Can you win him as an ally?
Survivors of the battle in Jade Forest have made their way to Kun-Lai Summit and are in dire need of your aid.
The Shado-Pan are mounting an incursion over the great wall into the Townlong Steppes. Assist them in this daring assault!
The Shado-pan of the great wall call for reinforcements against the mantid forces of the Dread Wastes. They need your help!

The Vale of Eternal Blossoms is under attack. Prince Anduin Wrynn requires your aid at the Temple of the White Tiger in Kun-Lai Summit to convince the peoples of Pandaria to allow outsiders access to the Vale so that they may help in its time of need.
The Vale of Eternal Blossoms is under attack. Sunwalker Dezco requires your aid at the Temple of the White Tiger.
Archmage Khadgar, hero of the Second War, is assembling a coalition of Azeroth's strongest to step through the Dark Portal.
ContinueDescription_lang: Help Archmage Khadgar fight the Iron Horde and shut down the Dark Portal inside Tanaan Jungle!

Description_lang: Archmage Khadgar, hero of the Second War, is assembling a coalition of Azeroth's strongest to step through the Dark Portal.
ContinueDescription_lang: Help Archmage Khadgar fight the Iron Horde and shut down the Dark Portal inside Tanaan Jungle!

Description_lang: Commander, Durotan calls for aid in leading a small strike team into Gorgrond to launch a counter attack against the Iron Horde stronghold there.
Commander, Yrel and Maraad call for aid in leading a small strike team into Gorgrond to launch a counter attack against the Iron Horde stronghold there.
The Iron Horde has made landfall in Talador and seeks to secure this crossroads territory from us. Commander, your forces are needed.
Spires of Arak is rife with war and rebellion. The exiles of the arakkoa are fleeing in droves and could prove valuable allies.
Commander, the Spires of Arak is rife with war and rebellion. The exiles of the arakkoa are fleeing the land in droves and could prove valuable allies.
The Iron Horde has made landfall in Talador and seeks to secure this crossroads territory from us. Commander, your forces are needed.
Thrall has called for aid in establishing a foothold at Nagrand, home of the dreaded Warsong and Burning Blade clans.
Vindicator Yrel has called for aid in establishing a foothold at Nagrand, home of the dreaded Warsong and Burning Blade clans.
The Warchief Vol'jin has come to your garrison to discuss invasion plans of Tanaan Jungle. Do your forces stand ready?
ContinueDescription_lang: Speak to Warchief Vol'jin inside your garrison to plan the invasion of Tanaan Jungle.

Description_lang: Fight Horde players for control of Arathi Basin in this resource-race battleground.
King Varian Wrynn has come to your garrison to discuss invasion plans of Tanaan Jungle. Do your forces stand ready?
ContinueDescription_lang: Speak to King Varian Wrynn inside your garrison to plan the invasion of Tanaan Jungle.

Description_lang: This ancient night elf temple has been overrun by the Twilight's Hammer. Defeat them before untold evils below are awoken!
The prisoners of the Stormwind Stockades are attempting to escape. Stop them!
Delve into the irradiated capital city of Gnomeregan to clean out its infestation of troggs, leper gnomes, and technological terrors.
The fiercest warriors of the Scarlet Crusade are raising an army within the Scarlet Halls. Defeat them before they can unleash their forces.
Attack the Scarlet Monastery, stronghold of the Scarlet Crusade, and bring justice to their zealous leaders within.
Travel into the crystal caverns of Maraudon where rumors claim a demonic presence has taken hold.
Adventure into the thorned nest of Razorfen Kraul, den and stronghold of the quilboar.
Adventure into the underground Foulspore Cavern to purge the corruption that grips the roots of Maraudon.
A hero is needed to bring an end to the corruption wrought by Princess Theradras and her minions within the caverns of Maraudon.
Explore Uldaman, the ruined city of the ancient Titans filled with a host of their failed creations and wondrous treasures.
Bring an end to the corrupted ancients and inhabitants that infest the eastern wing of ruins at Dire Maul.
A hero is needed to face the dreaded necromancers and their undead creations at their school of knowledge, Scholomance.
The elves' blind pursuit to regain their immortality led to a dark curse. Venture into the ruins of Dire Maul and put an end to it.
Undead sightings in this quilboar stronghold have given rise to the concern that the Scourge may be gaining a foothold in Kalimdor.
The brutal Gordok ogres have seized control of the northern wing of the Dire Maul and are exploiting the power within.
The once great human city of Stratholme is now a ruined nest of undeath. Only the bravest of heroes dare cross the front gate.
The once powerful and cruel sandfury trolls of Zul'Farrak appear to be amassing an army of undead. Will you stand against them?
A side entrance has been revealed into the ruined city of Stratholme.  Use it to launch an attack against the Scourge inside.
The Dark Iron Dwarves in Blackrock Depths are working with the Twilight's Hammer cultists and must be stopped.
Adventure into the Sunken Temple to put an end to the corrupted green dragon wardens there and stop the rogue Atal'ai troll priests.
Journey deep into the capital of the Dark Iron dwarves to do battle with their evil leader, Emperor Thaurissan.
Battle against the forces of the false horde united under the banner of Warchief Rend Blackhand and his black dragon allies.
Assault the nearly impenetrable bastion of the Fel Horde's base of operations in Hellfire Peninsula.
The Fel Horde is performing dark and disturbing experiments on their own people, forging fierce soldiers of war.
Liberate the captives of the sinister Coilfang naga in their Slave Pens in Zangarmarsh.
Adventure into the Underbog facing off against the strange fungal creatures of the deep.
Stop the scavenging ethereals under the banner of Nexus-Prince Shaffar from desecrating the draenei burial chambers within Auchindoun.
Explore the ancient Auchenai Crypts, battling the haunted draenei within and giving peace to its mad defenders.
Travel back in time to Old Hillsbrad Foothills where vile forces work to assassinate a young Thrall before he can come of age.
Battle the powerful magi of the arakkoa that have seized control of the Sethekk Halls.
Do battle with the blood elves within the Mechanar before they can unlock the mystical secrets of the naaru held within.
Kael'thas Sunstrider has revealed his allegiance to the Burning Legion and has retreated to Magisters' Terrace. He must be stopped!
Once thought to be abandoned, the ancient halls of Utgarde Keep once again thrive with the footsteps of vrykul warriors.
Malygos' forces are redirecting all arcane energies to the Nexus. They must be stopped before magic is removed from our world.
Journey into Azjol-Nerub, the once great spider empire that has become a web of undeath loyal to the Lich King.
Travel to the ancient underground city of Ahn'kahet where something terrible has been awoken in the depths of the world.
Assault the walls of Drak'Tharon Keep to do battle with the undead that are seizing control of the keep.
The Kirin Tor calls for aid as an invasion by the blue dragons threatens to release the most dreaded prisoners held within.
Adventure with famed explorer Brann Bronzebeard into the ancient titan foundry of the Halls of Stone.
The trolls of Gundrak are turning on their own gods, slaying them so that they might gain their power.
Storm Loken's stronghold and face him in his throne room within the Halls of Lightning.
The vrykul King Ymiron has returned and sworn loyalty to the Lich King. Defeat him before his army can reach full strength.
The blue dragonflight at the Oculus is working to channel all magic out of the world into the Twisting Nether and must be stopped.
Travel back in time to that fateful day when Prince Arthas rode his army into Stratholme before it could be consumed by the Scourge.
Deep within Blackrock Mountain, the Twilight's Hammer works with the forces of Deathwing to craft dangerous monstrosities.
Join forces with the elemental water lord Neptulon as he repels an invasion of the naga and their old god allies.
Journey into the elemental plane of air and do battle with the forces of Skywall and their storm drake allies.
The Twilight's Hammer cultists and their elemental perversions are fortified within the Stonecore on the elemental plane of earth.
The tol'vir followers of Neferset have been cured of their curse of flesh and threaten to crush the peace of the lands around them.
Invaders from the Twilight's Hammer have seized control of the dwarven city of Grim Batol and brought with them an ancient evil.
Adventure into the famed Stormstout Brewery and help restore order to the chaos that has broken out there.
Confront the Sha of Doubt as it tries to take hold of the Temple of the Jade Serpent.
The three great mogu clans that still hold sway in Pandaria have gathered in strength at the Mogu'shan Palace and must be stopped.
Confront the Sha of Violence, Anger, and Hatred, as they work to corrupt the ancient order of the Shado-pan to evil purpose.
Journey into the dreaded Bloodmaul Slag Mines to liberate the slaves of the ogres within.
The naval fleet of the Iron Horde is mustering at the Iron Docks in Gorgrond and must be stopped.
A hero is needed to repel the Shadow Council forces from the ancient draenei crypts at Auchindoun before they can turn the power there to evil.
Assault the Skyreach and the vile arakkoa there who are using the power of the sun against their enemies.
Fight other players in Skirmishes for the duration of this Bonus Event!
Fight other players in Battlegrounds for the duration of this Bonus Event!
Engage in Pet Battles for the duration of this Bonus Event!
Complete World Quests in the Dragon Isles for increased rewards for the duration of this Bonus Event!
RewardDescription_lang: Completing this quest will grant you renown with the Dragonflight faction of your choice!

Description_lang: Battle other players in 2v2 and 3v3 Skirmishes!
Claim Warsong Gulch for the Alliance in this capture-the-flag battleground.
Survivors of the battle in Jade Forest have made their way to Kun-Lai Summit and are in dire need of your aid.
Brewfest has come under attack by the Dark Iron Dwarves!  Take on their leader inside Black Rock Depths.
Head to Booty Bay and compete against other players in the Stranglethorn Fishing Tournament!  The contest starts at 2:00 pm.
Professions like Alchemy and Mining allow you to craft and gather useful items.  Talk to a guard in any capital city to find a trainer!
Our allies in the Cenarion Expedition require your aid in the swamps of Zangarmarsh.
Our allies in the Cenarion Expedition require your aid in the swamps of Zangarmarsh.
Your skills are needed in securing Terokkar Forest from the enemies of the Horde.
Your skills are needed in securing Terokkar Forest from the enemies of the Alliance.
The Mag'har of Garadar call for aid. Ride for Nagrand and bring the power of the Horde to their side.
The King has called for voluteers to negotiate with the Kurenai of Nagrand.
Secondary Professions like Cooking and Fishing are available to all characters.  Talk to a guard in any capital city to find a trainer!
Journey to the Blade's Edge Mountains, stronghold of the ogres and their gronn masters in Outland.
Journey to the Blade's Edge Mountains, stronghold of the ogres and their gronn masters in Outland.
Travel to the mana torn landscape of Netherstorm to do battle with demons, minions of Kael'thas, and defiant goblin rockets.
Travel to the mana torn landscape of Netherstorm to do battle with demons, minions of Kael'thas, and defiant goblin rockets.
The Alliance is amassing forces in the Dragonblight to stabilize the land and launch an offensive against the Lich King.
The Horde is amassing forces in the Dragonblight to stabilize the land and launch an offensive against the Lich King.
Heroes are needed to aid the Horde in establishing an outpost in the Grizzly Hills.
Heroes are needed to aid the Alliance in establishing an outpost in the Grizzly Hills.
The Knights of the Ebon Blade and the Argent Crusade need help in battle with the trolls of Zul'Drak and the invading scourge.
Visit the magical floating city of Dalaran in the skies above Crystalsong Forest.
The Darkmoon Faire has arrived!  Look for the portal to Darkmoon Island near Goldshire in Elwynn Forest.
The Darkmoon Faire has arrived!  Look for the portal to Darkmoon Island near Thunder Bluff in Mulgore.
Journey into the primal jungles of Sholazar Basin.
Journey into the primal jungles of Sholazar Basin.
Adventure awaits in the ancient titananic mountains of the Storm Peaks.
The King of Stormwind is preparing a team for an elite mission and requires your presence.
The yearly celebration of the fermented fruits of the harvest is happening right now!  Find the beer garden outside Ironforge.
RewardDescription_lang: You can win a variety of fun prizes like pets and seasonal garb!

Description_lang: The yearly celebration of the fermented fruits of the harvest is happening right now!  Find the beer garden outside Orgrimmar.
RewardDescription_lang: You can win a variety of fun prizes like pets and seasonal garb!

Description_lang: The sacred bonfires of Midsummer are threatened by Ahune, the Frost Lord!  Join other players and take him down.
Run a Warlords of Draenor dungeon in mythic difficulty to test your skill and receive improved rewards!
Battle Pet Training allows you to capture and level up unique pets!  Speak to Audrey Burnhep in Stormwind to learn this skill.
Battle Pet Training allows you to capture and level up unique pets!  Speak to Varzok in Orgrimmar to learn this skill.
Collect 100 unique pets to earn Nuts the squirrel!
Celebrate this holiday by honoring the sacred bonfires of Midsummer!  Speak to the Master Fire Juggler at a capital to learn more.
The Headless Horseman haunts the graveyards of the Scarlet Monastery during Hallow's End! Group up and hunt him down.
Battle other players inside a Rated Battleground!
Battle other players in 2v2 and 3v3 Arenas!
Visit any inn during Hallow's End to receive special treats!
Speak to Wagner Hammerstrike outside Ironforge and find out how you can pay tribute to one of the Alliance's greatest heroes.
Speak to Javnir Nashak outside Orgrimmar and find out how you can pay tribute to one of the Horde's greatest heroes.
The barriers between the spirit world and Azeroth are at their weakest!  Visit any capital city's graveyard to join the festivities!
The World of Warcraft Anniversary celebration is upon us!  Check your mail for a special gift.
Share in the Pilgrim's Bounty outside any capital city!
The most anticipated winter holiday is here!  You can find Greatfather Winter in Ironforge.
The most anticipated winter holiday is here!  You can find Great-father Winter in Orgrimmar.
Run Warlords of Draenor Heroic dungeons to test your skill and receive improved rewards!
Timewalk through Burning Crusade dungeons for the duration of this Bonus Event!
Timewalk through Wrath of the Lich King dungeons for the duration of this Bonus Event!
Timewalk through Cataclysm dungeons for the duration of this Bonus Event!

You can return to the Scouting Map in your Class Hall to choose assault point quests into different zones.

Run Legion Heroic dungeons to test your skill and receive improved rewards!

Use a Mythic Keystone at the entrance to a Mythic Dungeon for even greater challenges and rewards!
Return to your Class Hall and switch to a different specialization to begin the quest for that specialization's artifact.
Timewalk through Mists of Pandaria dungeons for the duration of this Bonus Event!
Descend into the Tomb of Sargeras to do battle with the dark force who leads the very Burning Legion.
Gather the armies of Legionfall and gain a foothold against the Legion on the Broken Shore.

Name_lang: Raid Finder: The Gates of Hell
Description_lang: After weeks of hard-fought battle, Azeroth's heroes at last enter the dark Tomb, but the Legion has been preparing as well...
Descend into the Tomb of Sargeras to do battle with the dark force who leads the very Burning Legion.

Name_lang: Raid Finder: Chamber of the Avatar
Description_lang: Aegwynn sealed away the defeated Avatar of Sargeras deep beneath the Tomb, but that fearsome husk now begins to stir....
In the depths of the Tomb of Sargeras, Kil'jaeden appears cornered at last. Or are we just playing into the Deceiver's hands?
Arathi Basin has been snowed in and covered with a thick fog of war.
Warsong Gulch goes crazy with three flags in play at once complete with scattered unique power-ups.
Kotmogu heats up with movement speed and the ability to pass the Orb to allies.
Gravity getting you down? Step into the Eye of the Storm and be prepared for a whole new en-lighten-ing experience.
Race to claim balls from the maps center and score points on your enemies' basket.
No mount? No problem. Grab a goat and head into mounted combat.
Up to 30 players clash in this packed Arena match.
Harken back to the early days in an epic tug-of-war battle.
Your 5-man arena team gets a sixth addition in the form of a boss. Defeat the enemies first to win!
A wonderful celebration of all things Moonkin is happening today in Moonglade. Stop by and see what you can learn!
Dust off those pauldrons and compete in a fashion competition of Azerothian proportions! Speak to a transmogrifier NPC in any major city to participate in the Trial of Style!
Join the Gnomes as they celebrate their unrelenting moxie! Race across the Eastern Kingdoms, from Gnomeregan down to Booty Bay!
The main auction houses in Orgrimmar and Stormwind have been cleaned out and turned into Dance Parties for the day! Crowd on in and show some faction pride!
The mages of Azeroth like to relax, too. Hop into a portal at your local watering hole and join the Tavern Crawl!

On this date, the Scarab Gong was rung, opening the gates of Ahn'Qiraj. Represent your faction by gathering supplies or by slaying Twilight and Qiraji forces. The winning faction gets to fly their banner next to the Scarab Gong for the rest of the year!
Today, the sporelings of Sporeggar in Zangarmarsh hold their annual mushroom festival. Help them keep the great Fshoo alive as long as possible!
Today is the day that the Frayfeather hippogryphs hatch.  Head to Frayfeather Highlands in Feralas to witness the spectacle firsthand!
Today, the baby Winterfin murlocs of Borean Tundra complete their trip across the Westrift.
The skies are clear, the wind is calm... it's a great day for hot air ballooning. Hop into a hot air balloon, enjoy the scenery, and make some new friends!
The citizens of Azeroth need a break. Let's go boating in Thousand Needles!
The dinosaurs in Un'goro are getting restless. Time to go pay them a visit!
Today, the denizens of Azeroth and Draenor take some time to celebrate the hard work that their guards perform. /salute a guard to show you care!
Group size shrinks down to an intimate 6v6 in selected battlegrounds

Name_lang: Raid Finder: Seat of the Pantheon
Description_lang: Lead the Army of the Light into battle against the Burning Legion in their hallowed capital to destroy them once and for all!
Lead the Army of the Light into battle against the Burning Legion in their hallowed capital to destroy them once and for all!
Join Alleria Windrunner in the ancient eredar seat of power where Prophet Velen, Archimonde, and Kil'jaeden once ruled to dispel the looming void threat.
Join Alleria Windrunner in the ancient eredar seat of power where Prophet Velen, Archimonde, and Kil'jaeden once ruled to dispel the looming void threat.

Answer Prophet Velen's call to take the war against the Legion to Argus.

Prophet Velen and members of the Army of the Light are behind enemy lines. High Exarch Turalyon needs your help to save them.
Magni has uncovered new information and has called you to speak with him once more.
Preparations have been made to begin the assault on Antorus. Meet with Magni before leading the charge.

Return to the classic Wrath of the Lich King raid to defeat Yogg-Saron.
Participate in the battle for the Seething Shore.
Participate in the battle for the Seething Shore.
In foul pits, far beneath the halls of Uldir, the source of the corruption that has befallen Zandalar awaits.
The remnants of old experiments gone awry litter the lower halls of Uldir, as a dark power stirs within the depths.
The doors of this ancient titan research facility open for the first time in millennia. What remains of the horrors sealed away?
The doors of this ancient titan research facility open for the first time in millennia. What remains of the horrors sealed away?

Run a random Battle for Azeroth dungeon to upgrade your character's gear!

Our war effort was successful. Report to the Port of Zandalar to launch the attack on Stromgarde! For the Horde!
Our war effort was successful. Report to Boralus Harbor for transport to the warfront. Your mission is to take back Stromgarde and rebuild it to it's former glory! For the Alliance!
Adventure awaits! Explore the islands around Kul Tiras and Zuldazar for Azerite and treasure. Report to the Port of Zandalar to ship out!
Adventure awaits! Explore the islands around Kul Tiras and Zuldazar for Azerite and treasure. Report to Boralus Harbor to ship out!
